Fetch

Windows

Workspace ONE Application Management Tool

Over 7500+ Applications

Fetch has a database of over 7500 Windows applications and a combined total of over 65,000 versions & architectures.

Over 5000+ Icons

Fetch now also has a repository of 5000+ App icons that are automatically uploaded to the Workspace ONE App Catalog.

Comprehensive Search

Search for an Application by name and automatically create its corresponding Native App in Workspace ONE UEM.

Identify Application Updates

Query your existing Workspace ONE UEM App Catalog and identify available updates from the Fetch database.

Upload your existing App Inventory

Upload an existing app inventory/report of your existing device management platform and identify which applications can automatically be uploaded to Workspace ONE UEM.

Upload your Existing Apps

Use Juice to scan an existing folder of your previously downloaded or internally packaged/developed applications and automatically upload them to Workspace ONE in bulk.
